{
  "stem": "1496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the deal was made, and the man survived the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So here you got one example how Schindler was always ready and willing to help anybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We saw Schindler.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I saw him daily.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, I came to the Schindler's factory when Schindler decided-- when he took over, it was a pots and pan, enamel pots and pans factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But he knew that by making pots and pans, the Nazis will not fight the war, so he established a munition department.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then when I came to Schindler's factory, this-- I worked in the munitions department, because, as you know, that some of the people came to Schindler's factory way back-- even they were going out from ghetto, already working for Schindler.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So when I came-- and this was 1943-- this was almost one-- one of the last group of people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He constantly requested-- by bribing, requested authority to get more and more people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You could-- I saw him daily, almost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "When he walked into the factory, you could already smell that he's around, because the perfume was all over the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was a heavy smoker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He used to give people cigarettes by lighting up a cigarette, taking a few puffs, and just throwing the cigarette on the ground, because he knew that some people were very anxious.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They were heavy smokers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They wanted a cigarette, but it was not available.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that's how he was giving out cigarette.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He used to buy food on the black market in order to subsidize the rations, because the rations were very small.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You know, we were talking about concentration-- the ration in concentration-- in Krakau-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
